oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Wally Fowler's All-Night Singing concert at the W. D. Packard Music Hall
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Gospel music; Negro spirituals (oral or performed works); Fowler, Wally; Cantrells (Musical group)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black on yellow) announcing Wally Fowler's Gospel and Spiritual All-Night Singing Concert with the Swanee River Boys, Loyce Jane Neal, Christian Troubadours, the Cantrell Family and others at the W. D. Packard Music Hall on January 31. Poster features metal photoplates of Wally Fowler and the Swanee River Boys.
